{"id": "1256039941583016078", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 0, "author_id": "190674373483429888", "author_name": ".weiyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "<:prsk_shiho:901451422430806056>", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T00:14:18.167000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256042857957953556", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 0, "author_id": "190674373483429888", "author_name": ".weiyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "互相尊重，請從自身做起，\n恕我眼拙，是真沒看出誰對你有明顯的輕視跟敵意，\n既然都說回歸討論，你這能氣到半夜睡不著是......\n\n坦白說你這樣給人的壓力很大，\n會讓人擔心是不是正常交談都能傷到你，\n如果你還想跟大家有正常交流的環境，望自重\n聊遊戲，聊想法，少上學術跟情緒", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T00:25:53.485000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256049026105741505", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "A.至少在我看來問對特定事件是否了解跟 你包含詢問學歷年紀在內的行為 有一定程度上的差異", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T00:50:24.086000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1256049025325465650", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 49286, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255487797800861766/1256049025325465650/image.png?ex=69cc6bcf&is=69cb1a4f&hm=32f04732a154788b51f13076acbb7430406adb54f9d636ffd0fb70c557a82d23&"}, {"id": "1256049025824849930", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 38494, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255487797800861766/1256049025824849930/image.png?ex=69cc6bd0&is=69cb1a50&hm=eaefd7ed5aa95c5f190907ec70e1f1529c6a5f6800e2f8cfb91d4e52339e0cb5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256049814739877929", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且實際上也沒用到多少微積分的內容吧，cra問偏微分究竟少了哪個維度你也沒回\n(然後是課綱不同嗎?之前應該更硬核吧，我記得我這屆是高一教基礎的微積分，高三教一些與大學相關的微積分內容", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T00:53:32.111000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256051879092158474", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "B. 在最前面我們應該是都有提到，我們認為沒有宗教干政，但是有權力更迭\n這是一開始的基礎，而且你後面是有對權力被影響的部分回復，因此可能認為你對這部分也有興趣而繼續討論\n(然後如果哪邊有你認為在輕視你的部分，可以提出哪邊有用詞不當的地方", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T01:01:44.291000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256052010709684246", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T01:02:15.671000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1256052010457759754", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 17500, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255487797800861766/1256052010457759754/image.png?ex=69cc6e97&is=69cb1d17&hm=16d3e0a84ba1cf22706c3ca3b5cab83021f4e65fa6e3b5530bb7a013c360501c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256052096915214348", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "應該是從這部分開始分成兩個討論面向\n然後佛教部分我認為是宗教方面地位的爭奪，與世俗權力無關，所以不叫宗教亂政(當然這只是我個人看法，或許其他人有不同見解，畢竟這方面我也不是專業的", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T01:02:36.224000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-28T01:10:37.406000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256053238491516961", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 0, "author_id": "711586313555410945", "author_name": "35sui", "author_bot": false, "content": "嗯…我認為就人類史而言，宗教對社會而言有兩種常見的模式。\n1. 宗教是政權的手段之一，用以鞏固統治\n2. 當然若政權腐敗，有的人會以神話宗教為由起義。如 趙匡胤（鴨王？）\n但若是要說宗教和政權可以相互對抗我覺得有點難，畢竟一國不太會有兩種聲音（當然歐洲可能有過這種情況，但通常都是在選擇繼任者時就開始權利傾尬，不太會有半途截胡的情況）", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T01:07:08.397000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256053353075708027", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 0, "author_id": "711586313555410945", "author_name": "35sui", "author_bot": false, "content": "說錯是朱元璋", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T01:07:35.716000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256069824539525262", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 19, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "A.看不懂你的A，附帶了一張截圖，文字敘述就斷了，截圖跟文字敘述我沒看出關聯性。\nB.cra問到少了哪個維度，我有說明過的：\n少了哪個維度，是由高維決定的；\n四維降三維，少掉的那個維度是甚麼，如果三維能夠有認知，那他就是圖魯；\n當他能夠影響到四維，那他就能成為四維生物，不管這四維生物是不是神，但一定不是人了。(神可以是4.5.6.7.8反正只說高維，沒說他幾維的)\nC.\"佛僧掌握國家大權\"，你可能漏看了這句，佛教干政了，後面神道也干政了...\n\n理性討論", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:13:02.819000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1256049026105741505", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256070122678911046", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "他舉的例子二維偏微分後還是二維啊", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:14:13.901000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256070265343840328", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "截圖部分很明顯你帶有的攻擊性更強，如果你覺得兩者是等同的那就好都沒任何歧視引戰，只是認為你的說法能再溫和點而已", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:14:47.915000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:16:06.395000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256071592178614404", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 19, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "這個例子明顯不適用於解說多維觀念，而且這是更深入的應用，我無法用他的舉例來說明\n語氣的部分，如果有冒犯到，我道歉...\n\n但我多問一個問題...不會微積分...不是很正常的事嗎？！還是說在我這個年代不會很正常，現在不一樣了？", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:20:04.257000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1256070122678911046", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256072051916279839", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 19, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "\"當一個人覺得所有人都在逆向的時候就該反思一下自己了\"，這句，超失禮...明明各位聊戰國聊得很開心，根本性的答非所問，卻說是我的問題...", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:21:53.867000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1256051879092158474", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256072205335531551", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 19, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "跟會不會無關吧，高中或大學畢業(看文理組)後通常就丟掉了，你再看下截圖認為你的問題僅是在\"不會微積分嗎\"", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:22:30.445000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["676337286769672192"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1256071592178614404", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256072500438106245", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "這部分你找他/管理看怎麼處理，我是覺得沒必要到這樣嗆人沒錯", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:23:40.803000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:23:46.707000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256073462246674495", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "然後對於你干政的定義還是不能夠清楚了解，是有動手就算嗎?還是要成功\n因為僧人的權力還是都還是來自於天皇(去搜了下確實有打算奪取皇位但即使是重臣也還是直接被流放了", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:27:30.116000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:30:01.657000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256074239891472394", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 19, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "你剪掉了引言...我上去找了，原話有引言的，因為他對於高維對低維無干涉表示不理解，所以我拿ABCD跟XYZ作說明，甚至更上面，有\"單位\"的解說，這樣才延伸到微積分的問題，你可能看的...片段了", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:30:35.521000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1256072205335531551", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256074527503548508", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 19, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "...我有說的，原本我用\"亂政\"，後來我說\"干政\"，只要有影響政權的都算...", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:31:44.093000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1256073462246674495", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256074984409927773", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 19, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "你覺得加上哪些引言會讓你那幾句正當性更佳就放一下，至少我沒看到有任何**需要打出截圖中那段文字的必要性**，況且他也沒不明白吧?是你們談論的點都不在同一處", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:33:33.028000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:34:10.862000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["676337286769672192"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1256074239891472394", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256075328489783316", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 19, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "沒必要了，不在一個認知區域，確實無須硬回到該區域；有興趣再另起話題吧...", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:34:55.063000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1256074984409927773", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256075659210522695", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 19, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "🤔 反正我上面就說了我對日本歷史不熟，你等看看他們是怎麼想的吧", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:36:13.913000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["676337286769672192"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1256074527503548508", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256080041100443758", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 19, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "是阿，聊遊戲，聊想法，我明明就是在這樣做的；我一直強調\"是活動劇情中，圖魯認知到神是高維生物\"，我認為這樣的設定很好，(這是遊戲)神不再是虛無信仰，與我解讀世界的方式是一樣的。(這是想法)\n\n各位可以說明各位對於神與圖魯的關係，多數引用克蘇魯神話，請問，我是否有反對過？我是不是都說，我不理解，可以換個方式說明嗎...之類的話\n\n那當我以科學向的角度解說(這就是我的想法阿)，各位可以不理解，可以不接受，但請問，該有的尊重呢？\n每次我遇到我不理解的問題或答案，我是否都以\"我不理解，麻煩重新說明\"之類的方式，那麼，請問，駁斥我對世界的解讀，是尊重的嗎？", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T02:53:38.637000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["190674373483429888"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1256042857957953556", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256083573069578281", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 0, "author_id": "611608223983599616", "author_name": "jackpot_7", "author_bot": false, "content": "討論還是開心為主 聊的不開心或許停止討論也是種選擇", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T03:07:40.724000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "wish", "emoji_id": "1236951537788649492", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1256099610171281468", "channel_id": "1255487797800861766", "type": 0, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "別人說的都可以不理解不接受\n自己說的就要被理解被接受\n6\n講個自己以為對的高維論都能質疑別人的學歷 \n說的自己好像多尊重人一樣\n可以再道德至高沒問題", "timestamp": "2024-06-28T04:11:24.267000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255487797800861766", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V1.4.3.5 在線維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
